{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-12_end","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":23,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-12_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"M8-7","storyName":"恶言，报应不爽","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"凯尔希与博士见到了石棺核心中，已成怪物的梅菲斯特。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-12_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-12","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":21,"next":23,"characters":["罗德岛干员","凯尔希","查德","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/55/Avg_bg_bg_graduate.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"character","id":10},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":11},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"牧群的强度非常高。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"萨卡兹的变异感染者拥有比普通牧群宿主更强大的恢复能力，他们的智力也更高。","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"但我们没有任何和他们交流的办法，他们好像......很怪，他们像是活在另一个地方。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"另外，这种变异迟早会出事。结晶增长率太高了。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"空气中结晶粉尘的密度在这里达到了最大。","id":19,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也就是说，也许牧群的操控者已经占据了切尔诺伯格核心城的石棺。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在我们看不见的地方，一切都在发生。","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我没办法想象我们后边会遇到什么了。","id":23,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......被骂也没关系，医生，我还是要说，这事太难了。","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我们可能在自杀。最关键的是，我真不觉得我们有本事救下这个城市和龙门什么的。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"27","text":"你这不是自降士气吗？"},"2":{"id":"27","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"27","text":"但我们有事要做。"}},"values":[],"id":26},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":27,"end":42},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"查德，我记得你有家室。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查德","text":"医生你还记得挺牢，但你记错了，老婆女儿都不要我了。我没有家。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"查德，你想过和她们再见面，和她们再一起生活下去吗？","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查德","text":"做梦倒是有做过。","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"把梦实现的第一步，就是让我们有做梦的机会。","id":37,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们停下切尔诺伯格，感染者就不会因此过得更坏。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"给你的女儿一个机会，查德。让她有机会再见见她的父亲。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查德","text":"......","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查德","text":"都听你的，医生。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_090.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":43},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"character","id":45},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/62/Avg_bg_bg_graduatecore.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":46},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":48},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"50","text":"你只是在哄骗他。"}},"values":[],"id":49},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":50},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我说的可能是假话，我不觉得这片大地会轻易变好，感染者们重回他们曾经生活的概率微乎其微。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但是我说的也可能是真话。","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"假设我们现在离开了，他就不会再有机会见到他的女儿，无论他的家人和他本人会不会在接下来的其他什么事故里丧生。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"假使我们无力解决我们现下遭遇的事件，更宽泛的学术研究就只会停留在理论层面。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"实施者成功的实践为我们提供了继续实践的资格。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"再多的感染者制度改革家，只需一次失败，这种资格将永久性地失效，我们也不会再有取回它的机会。","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果需要一个恰当的喻体，我会使用“生命”这个概念。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......每一次重大行动的成功都如同我们生命的延续，而失败则意味着死亡。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"科学里没有起死回生这个概念。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们只有一次机会去挽救自己的生命。我们会遭遇许多灾厄，每一次意外都会毁了自身，对于我们个人如此，对于罗德岛也如此。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"像切尔诺伯格事件这样的灾难，我们还会遇到许多次。但只要我们有一次没能解决这个问题，我们就会死。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"一方面，我们要在疾病追上我们大多数人前，阻止疾病；另一方面，我们要在风暴里拯救自己。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不会过分标榜罗德岛的作用。只是，现在，这里，只有我们能处理这个问题。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"绝大多数人都只有一次生命。一旦失去了，就是永远的失去。","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"67","text":"还有人有许多次生命？"}},"values":[],"id":66},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":67,"end":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"啊，我不是这个意思。我的意思是，有的人甚至从来没拥有过自己的生命。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"很多人从出生开始就没有沾染过正常的事物，扭曲的土地只有扭曲的收成。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"恶意汇聚在切尔诺伯格，正是因为有的恶意从未被遏止。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"恶意，事实上，恶意的链条不会自行消失。","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"一次破坏，一次谋杀，起因可能只是出自一丝渴望，在法律触及不到的土地上，野蛮自我生长，形成了独有的规律。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而这种规律比城邦的法律强上万分，因为它无法被毁灭。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"它就是暴力。我们血管中流淌的暴力，来自我们的生命中未遭文明驯化的部分。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"听。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你听见那......","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......歌声......？","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"奇怪，我理应不会被源石技艺带来的任何错觉干扰。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"干员们，加装防护设备！","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Dr.{@nickname} ,可能有一些不好的事情正在发生。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"虽然我们已经能从一路上的乱象得出同样的结论，但我们要面对的事情可能会比我们预想的更糟。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"84","text":"一直如此。"}},"values":[],"id":83},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":84,"end":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也不至于理所当然。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也许我们和这座城市都被诅咒了。但只要是诅咒，就能被解开。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"种下恶的种子就会开出恶的花朵，结下恶的苦果。如果我们用善意浇灌一片土地，那这片土地，哪怕不会好到哪里去......不管怎样，也不会沦落至斯，被这种惨状所淹没。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可惜......","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":90},{"type":"text","text":"你顺着凯尔希的视线望去。","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可惜，据我所知，邪恶往往会诞生更大的恶，而善良的人大多没能善终。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不能让你再去推动另一场噩梦，感染者。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":96},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"image","id":98}],"characters":["罗德岛干员","凯尔希","查德","？？？"]}